divs: sighting detailsit was around 11:25 pm on 3\31\12 was talking to my brother on the cell phone walking back home was in a empty parking lot where there is dollar general store.i walking past a street light in the parking lot,in the top field of my vision above the street light i noticed a white light i looked up thinking maybe a shooting star.but what i saw was the most unusual shaped outlined i ever seen.best way to describe it was the outline of huey type helicopter but just the "tail illuminated" with about 8 different very white lights evenly spaced out and with the a single light where the bottom of the body would be.the was no noise and nor do i live where the is a airport where they fly helicopters ,they just fly small cessna types crafts.like i said the whites were very white and not the type the use on any aircraft i ever seen.saw the object for just a few secs and then just disappeared
